<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Under Review - {{ siteName }}</title>
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            line-height: 1.5;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .kb-pending {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 480px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .kb-pending-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: #fff3e0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.75rem;
        }

        .kb-pending h1 {
            font-size: 1.375rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .kb-pending p {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .kb-status-detail {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
            background: #fafafa;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .kb-status-detail strong {
            color: #333;
        }

        .kb-badge-pending {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.125rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            background: #fff3e0;
            color: #e65100;
        }

        .kb-footer a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
            background: #1a56db;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background 0.15s;
        }

        .kb-footer a:hover {
            background: #1648b8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="kb-pending">
        <div class="kb-pending-icon">&#9203;</div>

        <h1>Your Application Is Under Review</h1>
        <p>Thank you for applying to our affiliate program. Your application is currently being reviewed by our team.</p>
        <p>We will notify you once a decision has been made.</p>

        <div class="kb-status-detail">
            <strong>Status:</strong> <span class="kb-badge-pending">{{ affiliate.affiliateStatus|capitalize }}</span>
            <br>
            <strong>Applied:</strong> {{ affiliate.dateCreated|date('M j, Y') }}
        </div>

        <div class="kb-footer">
            <a href="/">Return to Homepage</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
